sentences.english: The facility, to be built in Qinhuangdao, will be the first of its kind in the region.
sentences.chinese: 秦皇岛的这个设施将成为该地区第一个此类培训中心。

sentences.english: Inter-Provincial shuttle from Beijing to Qinhuangdao is provided.
sentences.chinese: 从北京首都机场到秦皇岛可以乘坐机场大巴。

sentences.english: Which Qinhuangdao marriage yarn store sex price is comparatively high?
sentences.chinese: 秦皇岛哪家婚纱店性价比比较高？

sentences.english: Finally, this paper has carried on the empirical analysis take the Qinhuangdao administrative service center as the example.
sentences.chinese: 最后，以秦皇岛市政务服务中心为例进行了实证分析。

sentences.english: Beidaihe is located in the west part of Qinhuangdao City, in Hebei Province.
sentences.chinese: 北戴河海滨在河北省秦皇岛市的西部。

sentences.english: The efficacy of frequently-used 8 coccidiostats in Qinhuangdao area was evaluated.
sentences.chinese: 对秦皇岛市场上常用的8种抗球虫药的药效作了评价。

sentences.english: Fishing boats in the distance off Qinhuangdao can also be seen if you've got good eyesight.
sentences.chinese: 如果你视力够好的话，可以看到远处秦皇岛的打渔船。

sentences.english: Qinhuangdao city is a important harbour city of the economic zone round Bobal sea in China.
sentences.chinese: 秦皇岛市是我国环渤海经济区的重要港口城市。

sentences.english: This membership card can only be used in QinHuangDao school.
sentences.chinese: 此卡只限于会员本人于秦皇岛学校使用。

sentences.english: The results indicate that there is small impact of eco-city planning on the environment in Qinhuangdao city.
sentences.chinese: 结果表明，秦皇岛市生态城市规划环境影响较小。

sentences.english: The train carried coal to Qinhuangdao and then deadheaded back to Tianjin to pick up another load.
sentences.chinese: 这火车先把煤运至秦皇岛，然后放空车到天津载货。

sentences.english: A coal trader at Qinghuangdao Harbor said.
sentences.chinese: 秦皇岛港一位煤炭贸易商说。

sentences.english: The ship entered Port Qinhuangdao at dawn.
sentences.chinese: 这艘船在黎明时驶入秦皇岛港。

sentences.english: Beijing-Qinhuangdao cars per hour class one.
sentences.chinese: 北京至秦皇岛的汽车每小时一班。
